{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_016", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雷欧在森林中救了一只被陷阱困住的白狐，白狐离开前回头看了他一眼。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "白狐其实是精灵族的斥候，她引来了精灵援军，在关键时刻救了雷欧的命。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_017", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "城堡的地下室里有一扇锁着的铁门，钥匙在国王的保险柜里。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "铁门后是一条通往城外的密道。王国被围时雷欧通过密道搬来了援军。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_018", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "梅林法师的魔法书上有一页是空白的，怎么也显示不出内容。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "空白页需要在满月之夜用龙血涂抹才能显示——那是一道禁咒的咒语。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_019", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "铁匠铺里挂着一把锈迹斑斑的巨剑，矮人铁匠说没人能拔得动它。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雷欧在生死关头拔出了这把剑——它是上古英雄的佩剑，只有纯洁之心才能驾驭。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_020", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "精灵公主总是在深夜独自弹奏一首哀伤的曲子。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "曲子里隐藏着精灵族圣地的坐标——那是能治愈一切诅咒的生命之泉所在地。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_021", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "酒馆老板总是把同一个座位留给'老朋友'，即使那个座位空了很多年。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "'老朋友'其实是失踪多年的前冒险者，他在一次任务中受了重伤，被老板救下后隐姓埋名。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_022", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "冒险者公会的公告板上总贴着一张泛黄的寻人启事。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "寻人启事要找的人其实还活着，他是被龙族囚禁在龙巢中的人类使者。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_023", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雷欧的剑上刻着一行小字，他从来没注意过。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "小字是用上古精灵语写的——'此剑的主人将肩负拯救世界的使命'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_024", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "魔法学院图书馆的最深处有一本禁书，只有校长能借阅。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "禁书中记载了击败魔王的唯一方法——需要集齐七件神器。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_025", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "矮人铁匠每次喝醉都会说'那座火山要醒了'，没人当真。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "火山其实是远古火龙的巢穴。龙醒来时火山就会喷发。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_026", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王宫花园中有一棵枯死的橡树，园丁说它是在一夜之间枯萎的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "橡树下埋着一块被诅咒的黑曜石，正是它在吸取大地的生命力。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_027", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "梅林的水晶球最近总是显示一片模糊的红色。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "红色预示着血月降临——那是魔王封印最弱的时刻，也是他试图回归的时机。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_028", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雷欧救了一个被山贼追杀的陌生人，陌生人说会报答他。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "陌生人其实是邻国的王子，他后来带着军队回来帮助雷欧对抗魔王军。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_029", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "精灵族的生命之树开始枯萎，长老们束手无策。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "生命之树的根部被一种暗影毒素侵蚀了，这是魔王的黑魔法造成的。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_030", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雷欧在梦中总是听到一个声音在呼唤他的名字。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "声音来自一把封印在圣山中的神剑，它在寻找能将它拔出的人。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_031", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "酒馆里有一个沉默寡言的吟游诗人，从不唱关于自己的歌。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "吟游诗人其实是王国通缉的叛军领袖，他用吟游诗人的身份作掩护。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_032", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "城堡的护城河中有时候会浮起一些银色的鱼鳞。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "护城河底有一条水下通道通往城外，那些鱼鳞是从人鱼身上掉落的。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_033", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "雷欧在冒险中得到了一颗龙的眼球，据说可以看透一切幻象。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "龙的眼球在对抗魔王时发挥了关键作用——它看穿了魔王的伪装幻术。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_034", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "公主的项链上挂着一颗蓝色的宝石，她说那是母亲留给她的。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宝石中封印着一只凤凰的灵魂，在公主遇险时它会释放出守护的力量。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_035", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "兽人部落的萨满说预言中的'天选者'即将降临，部落将迎来变革。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "天选者是一个人类和兽人的混血儿，他将打破两个种族之间的隔阂。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
